&lt;li&gt;How to identify and disrupt problematic patterns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our favorite strategies that you can implement immediately so you can add &amp;quot;no&amp;quot; to your vocabulary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
