&lt;p&gt;Basic familiarity with R is recommended to get the most out of the Boot Camp.If you have not used this platform before or need a refresher, step through the tutorials outlined below so you have the basic skills needed for Boot Campsuccess.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each participant is required to have a personal laptop/computer and a free, basic RStudio Cloud account. All lab sessions will be done using RStudio Cloud.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
